Author: pokipokitoki
Text: This is what I've been doing. It feels...great, but still disordered? I think if I explained it to non-ED folk, they wouldn't understand why it's bad and they'd probably praise me for my "healthy eating habits". I feel like I'm constantly walking a tightrope to stay exactly where I am in order to not let things completely spiral out of control. I can feel it in my bones that this time around, there is a high risk of serious, permanent physical complications or death if I do let that happen.
